ndhcpd (0.2.0-trusty1) trusty; urgency=medium

  * Add PVS-Studio support
  * warning: V572 It is odd that the object which was created using 
    'new' operator is immediately cast to another type.
  * error: V730 Not all members of a class are initialized inside 
    the constructor. Consider inspecting: server_id.
  * Fix mask on pipe creation
  * Cosmetic changes
  * Move local CMake modules to cmake/Modules directory
  * Remove 'User Installation' option and service file setting
  * Pretty print CMakeLists.txt file
  * Add config.h file support
  * Export *.cmake files
  * Eliminate major version from library name
  * Add log4cpp support

